      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "rationale": "Input parameters used in the CFD model were not formally reconciled against the experimental test rig settings. Rotational speed tolerance and inlet flow measurement uncertainty were not cross-checked."
    }
