    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors were assessed. Seven factors achieved levels below the required level for MRL 5; six factors showed significant gaps. Despite these deficiencies the model is provisionally accepted subject to remediation of the identified gaps prior to regulatory submission. Monte Carlo UQ results provide partial confidence in the hemolysis predictions within the nominal operating envelope.",
